Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,JOHN'S DECISION! PROTECT THE MINE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lassie, you look busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is, it has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Today it was exactly on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, it came, it came!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it know exactly when John come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Spinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will leave this school soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father who worked in the mine\Ndecided to resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll stop working at the Wellington Coal Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was looking for work elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My father works harder in this business\Nthan any other work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and this work is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... maybe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,John is lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie goes with him wherever he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad, are you there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be another possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you John?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm is a bit busy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to go tomorrow\Nfor fishing because it is vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fishing?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you prepared the tools? Should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised you for tomorrow already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just had this pile of books\Nso I decided to read them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the Wellington Coal Mine\Nis in trouble, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear this talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From Spinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiner's father is looking for another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He will soon resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He is looking for another job...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal output may have been\Nfewer recently but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? I'm sure that the next\Noutputs will be better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Certainly?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what the manager\Nand all the miners say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We will succeed without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's plenty of coal waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you read these books!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go fishing when you\Nget out a lot of charcoal again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good night!\N- Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom's in a night shift, let's go Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We seem to be going to stop working next week.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what will happen to us\Nwhen we resume work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get the salary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing everything I can,\Nso I'll talk to the president about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the coal... come out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it will come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose it didn't come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough told us it would come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust what Mr. Carraclough says!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my household savings are now over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week we will not be able to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can believe in the work we do together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I also expected to be just soil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I can't just judge this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal didn't come out! And you can't!\NWhat to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This analysis is not very accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ask me to give you urgent\Nresults and perhaps make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, isn't there some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say anything now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you dig for a longer time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't check the condition of the layer,\Nwe will not come to a conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They must conclude quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so we won't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coal is supposed to exist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This layer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This indicates that the range\Nis becoming relatively narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My God! My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think the coal layer is not over yet,\Nso we have to think of something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked in the coal mine for almost 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The results were very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time different, the coal\Ndidn't come out suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, each coal layer exits\Nthe other coal 5 yards away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have the same experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As old people say, it's very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be optimistic\Nbut this is unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is 5 yards away, but in fact the\Ndistance has swelled to 20 yards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think previous experiences won't work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a possibility that coal will come out\Nwhen we dig larger than the usual layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You, do you consider yourself a geologist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it me or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad! Bad! Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here, we can rely on Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At least he should be able to come here,\Neven though he is a university lecturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait Lassie! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Is it your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So John...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog looks very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you really like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I like dogs very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even his hair type is very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I brush it daily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for interrupting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to see you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I like to praise you... Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Colin here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my house doesn't need\Nanything like that, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about coal? There's no way to get it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I got any message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I also expected no benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the third time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't lose hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you will find\Na good job in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Spinner seems to have already moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't know yet when that will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that his father\Nsuddenly found a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't say goodbye to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't say "farewell" to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,John and Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't move to another place when\Nyour father changes his work, does you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What strange words do you say, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hm?\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Close?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the result of the\Nrealization of that world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that the owner is the one\Nwho published this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a report be published because\Nof such a simple investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have reached another conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I really say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the authority to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Sam! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But Duke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at this article, you may find the\Npossibilities of returning a coal mine to Wellington!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the life is simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe the reports of the experts\Nor the words of the responsible director?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, but I'm very busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the number of mine workers\Nwho despaired of coal mining?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to work quickly without interest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even know if they\Ncan get the money or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you want to reduce the salaries of miners?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that? Don't you think\Nthat it's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, is not your son's name John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your son's dog named Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very good dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I also love dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of my folks love kennel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course when the mine closes you\Nwill need money for your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Don't you want\Nto make a bargain with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for that, but I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie is the friend of my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gave it to me, it would be\Nthe best dog in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, will you give up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Duke also said in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, wouldn't you be able to extract coal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if you investigated more precisely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came to this village you\Nworked at the Wellington Coal Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for 15 years and faced many problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best to solve such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always getting ready for things\Nlike that, wasn't you, Sam Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone was doing their best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For this you work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to work hard with everyone to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will check the data again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you John!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's my father's lunch!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam is in the mine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In the mine? My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I will keep his food in his office!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he is doing his best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My father works in the depths\Nof the earth to achieve his goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The size is 16 and 25 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The number 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Between them one point?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is 8.5 inches!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,8.5 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, don't lose to those scientists!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from the hard worker,\Nyour influence will not affect you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He have finally slept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How it was?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected, he can't trust my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hm...\N- Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I see my father doing this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what outcome\Nhe has achieved in his work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm running away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have decided to make your family happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Hamilton, in your new city!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it, everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do your best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take care of yourself!\N- Live well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who will leave next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we worked for a long\Ntime in the mine together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He had to listen to Sam's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Duke of Rudling is the grandfather of Priscilla
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the man who praised you, remember him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll understand if he looks at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You came to show me Lassie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate how many times\NI said it's still a good dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's wrong!\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood, I knew you\Nwould say something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you listen to my father again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your father ask you to come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My father didn't tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at my father,\NI can't remain silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what my father has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get in too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is shut down the mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to rely
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on the results of unreliable investigations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you handle things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're a smart boy\Nwho understands the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still want you to reconsider that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will not know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that coal will come out or not\Nbefore you try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have money to build\Na big palace like you, Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't own a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though all this is destined for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do anything to keep\Nthe Wellington Coal Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you can take responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Responsability?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that I'm talking about\Na serious and important subject
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that concerns the fate of many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know perfectly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are met with responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This palace, the monastery,\Nall the buildings, companies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone are concerned\Nabout this important talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm responsible for all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if coal will come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like gambling or something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to deal\Nwith such important things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to try sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your precious thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For example the precious thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you undoubtedly have is Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you have to give it up, will you agree?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal... as my father said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely will come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep your word
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as you promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then you will return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be patient until the time comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad, he'll definitely\Nget out the coal, won't he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must do anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will help everyone with anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They will move Lassie to Scotland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NDO YOUR BEST, JOHN, AND PROTECT LASSIE!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
